title: Toilet by Hjultorv
shortdescription: Accessible toilet. The facility is located between Hjultorv and St. Hjultorvgyde behind Café Morville. Most easily accessed from St. Hjultorvgyde.

title: Parking ground at Preislers Plads
shortdescription: 277 parking spaces laid out as outdoor bays as well as underground parking facility. Motor-cycle parking and disabled parking available.

title: Parking facility at Fischers Plads
shortdescription: 479 parking spaces on an upper deck as well as underground parking – outside and inside. Motor-cycle parking and disabled parking available.

title: P-pladser at Domkirkepladsen
shortdescription: 59 parking spaces. Motor-cycle parking and disabled parking available.
